name: ABC
text:
"To know her is to love her. She's so much like me, but she's so much better than me."

Breonna Taylor's mother Tamika Palmer and other loved ones share about her impact, during an ABC News and Courier Journal special. #ABC2020. #SayHerName #BreonnaTaylor https://t.co/2XWspbqUV4 https://t.co/XO2rAqLjZd
